{"tid":13280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【煮「煲仔飯」】大懵阿媽　電飯煲放落電爐加熱","createTime":"2016-11-30T03:46:10.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T13:08:58.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"14b5d863fe6559c2b43d29b78aa1fa9e72ba8a0e","tid":13280,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:46:10.000Z","msg":"【地獄廚神】阿媽唔識用電飯煲 搞成咁點算好？ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n地獄廚神已恐怖，如果地獄廚神是一位媽媽，又會如何呢？外國一位網民便目擊自己「地獄廚神母親」的強大破壞力，竟然可以「煮熔電飯煲」。有網民看罷形容，沒想過這樣可以一舉毀壞兩件電器。 <br />\n<br />\n「地獄廚神」的兒子尤埃德（Uedn）將照片上載到討論區Reddit，可見電飯煲底部的塑膠已經熔解，而電熱爐上亦黏著不少熔解的塑膠。 <br />\n<br />\n究竟「地獄廚神媽媽」用了甚麼方法呢？尤埃德表示，原來其媽媽竟將只須插電、按掣如此簡單操作的電飯煲，放在電熱爐上「烹煮」，故煮熔了電飯煲底的塑膠，但不幸中之大幸是未釀成火災，「我不認為我母親明白電飯煲如何運作」。事發後，廚房充滿惡臭氣味，即使當地天氣寒冷，仍要打開窗戶通風。"},{"pid":"87c2ec5cd90ad8f67f2077525d9df371dfa2a677","tid":13280,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:47:24.000Z","msg":"網民對Uedn的遭遇都深表同情，「想清除電熱爐上熔掉的塑膠，就等同想用鐵鏟砍掉一棵樹。」尤埃德「神回覆」稱，兩母子用刀便輕易清除塑膠，但他幾乎被母親掉下來的刀子插中腳，故完全了解「母親在廚房有一點危險」。 <br />\n英國《每日鏡報》／Reddit <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20161130/55980787\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20161130%2F55980787&d=bTkwEGnHH2OXdpYsGZaakksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=b324b026\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20161130%2F55980787&h=efc6c661\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20161130/55980787</a>"},{"pid":"d4f0b840f971cef87fa66dc823f5b99f4a789dac","tid":13280,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:48:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c33533c58ba828efe390a1d169d1d9f3f2c62ea","tid":13280,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T07:35:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75a329a6f841296d34fdb384304793311bad2c24","tid":13280,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T13:00:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eee6636c38e05976c33cc7f93c9e863e48f8818b","tid":13280,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T13:07:03.000Z","msg":"都係食過第二啲野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"506898c5ff2c78d510403f04800b55f3856c4554","tid":13280,"uid":13082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T13:08:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}